hopobject.body: Looking for a job geraldton medical group Victoria's Secret model Marisa Miller is showing some skin – to get people to protect theirs. The 32-year-old hottie took it off for designer Marc Jacobs for the latest edition of his 'Protect the skin you’re in' T-shirts, part of the celebrity designer's skin cancer awareness campaign. On the shirt, Miller is pictured with the campaign's slogan and her hair strategically covering her X-rated parts.
